          SHORT="exFAT filesystem userspace utilities"

cat << EOF
As new exfat filesystem is merged into linux-5.7 kernel, exfatprogs is created
as an official userspace utilities that contain all of the standard utilities
for creating and fixing and debugging exfat filesystem in linux system.
The goal of exfatprogs is to provide high performance and quality at the level
of exfat utilities in windows.
EOF
